<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; padding: 30px; text-align: center; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        .content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 40px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); display: inline-block; max-width: 500px; }
        .button {
            background-color: #a91e6a;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .name { color: #a91e6a; font-weight: bold; text-transform: capitalize; }
        .warning { font-size: 13px; color: #666; font-style: italic; }
        .footer { margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px; }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content">
          <h2>Password Reset</h2>
          <p class="name">Hello, {{displayName}}!</p>
          <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account on <b>Kingdom of Drama</b>.</p>
          <p>Click the button below to set a new password:</p>

          <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">Change Password</a>

          <p class="warning">This link is valid for 15 minutes only.</p>
      </div>
        <p>If you did not make this request, simply ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>
        <small class="warning">This is an automated message, please do not reply.</small>
        <div class="footer">
            Kingdom of Drama Team &copy; 2026. All rights reserved.

        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
